&lt;p&gt;Abby and I did a tiny short hike together in &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.alleghenycounty.us/parks/bpfac.aspx&#34;&gt;Boyce Park&lt;/a&gt;. We&amp;rsquo;ve barely done any hiking at all this year, because of her accident breaking a foot and my doing the Pittsburgh Marathon and then getting poison ivy on a hike I did with a friend last month.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;We thought we&amp;rsquo;d combine a hike with a trip to Monroeville to &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.patelbros.com/&#34;&gt;Patel Brothers&lt;/a&gt; to buy Indian groceries and then eat at &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.udipicafepittsburgh.com/&#34;&gt;Udipi Cafe&lt;/a&gt;, so we did.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;It was good to be out together again. We miss hiking so much.&lt;/p&gt;

